N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 40.25 - Prior assessments

State Regulations

Any assessments paid to the commissioner by cooperative
associations prior to the effective date of this Part to defray the expense of
promulgating, administering and enforcing the order until such time as the
assessment as provided pursuant to section
40.23
of this Part is adequate for
that purpose shall be reimbursed to such cooperative associations from the
funds received and deposited by the commissioner in the dairy promotion fund
pursuant to section
40.24
of this

Part. Notes
